snippet.title: Eldrum: Untold - Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Eldrum: Untold has officially launched! The game is free to try, with single in-app purchase which unlocks the full game. Download links:

App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1486667077
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.gotterdammerung.untold
